envDataArray Get an array of environmental data from presence-absence points.

envDataArray.Rd

envDataArray Get an array of environmental data from presence-absence points.

Usage

envDataArray(occ, envData)

Arguments

occ

Occurence data frame. Should contain longitude and latitude columns

envData

List of environmental variables time series stack.

Value

An array of M points times N time steps times P environmental variables

Examples

occ <- mus_virtualis[1:5, ]
bio1_ts <- terra::unwrap(cmcc_cm_bio1)
envData <- list(bio1 = bio1_ts)
envDataArray(occ, envData)
